##3. Create a Jenkins Pipeline with Build → Test → Deploy stages, each printing its stage name.##

Jenkins → New Item → name it → choose Pipeline → OK.
In the job config, under Pipeline → Definition select Pipeline script.
Paste the Jenkinsfile content above into the script box → Save → Build Now.

pipeline {
  agent any

  stages {
    stage('Build') {
      steps {
        echo 'Build'
      }
    }

    stage('Test') {
      steps {
        echo 'Test'
      }
    }

    stage('Deploy') {
      steps {
        echo 'Deploy'
      }
    }
  }
}
